Fixed: Unique ID name lookup is not performed until ids tab is selected
Fixed: Unique ID name lookup is not performed when playing offline games
Fixed: Residual players that disconnect before loading the map will get correct weapons
Fixed: Fuel and select areas not being marked correctly on non-square maps
Fixed: Server refusing to allow move when client is trying to use all available fuel 
Fixed: When balancing teams bots will not leave until the beginning of the next round

